Incident_Report: Multiple reports of wildfires in different locations: Pine Forest, Route 20 and 2211 Grace Underpass.
Unit_Dispatch_Instructions: Forest Fire Unit 5 and Helicopter Water Drop dispatched to Pine Forest, Route 20. Deploy additional aerial firefighting units to 2211 Grace Underpass. Immediate evacuation advised for both areas.
Evacuation_Advisories: Mandatory evacuation for areas near Pine Forest, Route 20 and 2211 Grace Underpass
